    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1869-11-11T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1869-11-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="454" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d454">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Fish</persName>,
                                    Secretary of State, to Mr. <persName type="to">Robeson</persName>, Secretary of the Navy.</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <placeName>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of
                                        State</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                    </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1869-11-11">
                        <hi rend="italic">November</hi> 11,
                                    1869</date>.</dateline>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to inclose herewith a
                                transcript of a communication from the United States marshal for the
                                southern district of New York, of yesterday’s date, and will thank
                                you to inform me if a vessel subject to the orders of the Navy
                                Department can, without detriment to the public service, be directed
                                to assist the marshal in preventing the departure from New York, or
                                that vicinity, of any unlawful expeditions in aid of the Cuban
                                insurgents, to which the marshal refers, as believed to be in course
                                of preparation.</p>
                <p>I have the honor to be, &amp;c.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>HAMILTON FISH.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">Geo. M. Robeson</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Secretary of the Navy.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
